---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>
  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="pill">Astro + Bun + Vercel</div>
      <h1>Shipping the first version of `labdm-blog`.</h1>
      <p>
        This repository now starts from a minimal Astro app with a Bun-first
        workflow, GitHub branch protection on <code>main</code>, and a Vercel
        deployment pipeline ready to be connected with project secrets.
      </p>

      <div class="grid">
        <article class="card">
          <strong>Framework</strong>
          Astro is configured for a static Vercel deployment.
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <strong>Package Manager</strong>
          Bun manages installs, scripts, and the lockfile.
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <strong>Delivery Flow</strong>
          Pull requests run validation before merge, and deploy jobs can run once
          Vercel secrets are added.
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
